Extension:
==========
* Get user's external IP & additional info (location, flag, reverse-domain).
* Rewrite CoNetServ API (OOP), split NPAPI tools and JS tools.
* URL validator (regexp).
* Mozilla Firefox add-on updates.
* Google Chrome extension updates.

Plugin:
=======
* Rewrite API (each command should be object property to JS front-end).
* Get rid of GNU LIB IDN unnecessary mess, put it's files into
  the separate directory.
* URL validator (after the punycode conversion).
